column2: Q01‑F If the system offers a step‑by‑step wizard that helps club leaders create events quickly and correctly, how do you feel?
column3: Q01‑D  If the system does NOT provide a step‑by‑step event‑creation wizard and leaders must enter all details manually, how do you feel?
column4: Q02‑F  If club treasurers can see budget balances update instantly after each transaction, how do you feel?
column5: Q02‑D  If budget balances update only after several hours or days, how do you feel?
column6: Q03‑F  If you can search and filter campus venues by capacity, location, and available dates, how do you feel?
column7: Q03‑D  If there is no searchable venue database and venue details must be found manually, how do you feel?
column8: Q04‑F  If members can RSVP for club events online with one click, how do you feel?
column9: Q04‑D  If there is no online RSVP function and members must sign up through other means, how do you feel?
column10: Q05‑F  If event attendance can be recorded instantly by scanning a QR code or tapping NFC, how do you feel?
column11: Q05‑D  If attendance is recorded using paper lists or manual entry only, how do you feel?
column12: Q06‑F  If treasurers can export all financial records to CSV for analysis, how do you feel?
column13: Q06‑D  If financial data cannot be exported and must be copied manually, how do you feel?
column14: Q07‑F  If prospective members can submit a membership request online, how do you feel?
column15: Q07‑D  If prospective members have to apply in person or by email only, how do you feel?
column16: Q08‑F  If each user sees a personalised dashboard with upcoming events, role tasks, and budget graphs, how do you feel?
column17: Q08‑D  If the system has no personal dashboard and users must navigate multiple pages for this information, how do you feel?
column18: Q09‑F  If the system sends you reminders for events you marked as Interested"
column20: Q09‑D  If the system does not send reminders for your Interested" events
column22: Q10‑F  If members can message each other within the system, how do you feel?
column23: Q10‑D  If there is no internal messaging and members must use external apps, how do you feel?
column24: Q11‑F  If officers can bulk‑upload or download the membership list via Excel/CSV, how do you feel?
column25: Q11‑D  If membership data must be added or extracted one record at a time, how do you feel?
column26: Q12‑F  If you can subscribe to an ICS feed and see approved events in your personal calendar, how do you feel?
column27: Q12‑D  If you cannot subscribe and must manually add events to your calendar, how do you feel?
column28: Q13‑F  If the system automatically promotes wait‑listed members when seats open, how do you feel?
column29: Q13‑D  If wait‑listed members must be added manually when seats open, how do you feel?
column30: Q14‑F  If you can attach documents and images to requests via simple drag‑and‑drop, how do you feel?
column31: Q14‑D  If you must navigate file‑pickers or email documents separately, how do you feel?
